01:12:29,611 --> 01:12:31,946
It's all right.

870
01:12:56,105 --> 01:12:59,273
<i>Lawyer:
So, david, I want
to get you now</i>

871
01:12:59,341 --> 01:13:01,576
<i>To the year 2000.</i>

872
01:13:05,447 --> 01:13:07,815
Um,

873
01:13:07,883 --> 01:13:10,918
If I could have
some water?

874
