Right away.

875
01:13:22,197 --> 01:13:24,198
Thank you for coming
on such short notice.

876
01:13:24,266 --> 01:13:26,868
<i>Due to new evidence</i>

877
01:13:26,935 --> 01:13:28,436
<i>And a close look
at the case,</i>

878
01:13:28,504 --> 01:13:30,772
