01:15:33,595 --> 01:15:35,296
<i>David:
Uh, yeah.</i>

915
01:15:35,364 --> 01:15:38,599
Yeah well, just be sure
and turn the hall light off

916
01:15:38,667 --> 01:15:41,869
<i>When you're coming and leaving,
